31 void execute(const smacc_odom_tracker::OdomTrackerGoalConstPtr& goal) // Note: "Action" is not appended to DoDishes here
32 {
33  try
34  {
35  switch(goal->command)
36  {
37  case OdomTrackerGoal::RECORD_FORWARD_PATH:
38  odomTracker.setWorkingMode(WorkingMode::RECORD_PATH_FORWARD);
39  break;
40 
41  case OdomTrackerGoal::CLEAR_PATH_BACKWARDS:
42  odomTracker.setWorkingMode(WorkingMode::CLEAR_PATH_BACKWARD);
43  break;
44 
45  case OdomTrackerGoal::IDLE:
46  odomTracker.setWorkingMode(WorkingMode::IDLE);
47  break;
48 
49  case OdomTrackerGoal::START_BROADCAST_PATH:
50  odomTracker.setPublishMessages(true);
51  break;
52 
53  case OdomTrackerGoal::STOP_BROADCAST_PATH:
54  odomTracker.setPublishMessages(false);
55  break;
56 
57  case OdomTrackerGoal::PUSH_PATH:
58  odomTracker.pushPath();
59  break;
60 
61  case OdomTrackerGoal::POP_PATH:
62  odomTracker.popPath();
63  break;
64 
65  default:
66 
67  ROS_ERROR("Odom Tracker Node - Action Server execute error: incorrect command - %d", goal->command);
68  as_->setAborted();
69  }
70 
71  // never reach succeded because were are interested in keeping the feedback alive
72  as_->setSucceeded();
73  }
74  catch(std::exception& ex)
75  {
76  ROS_ERROR("Odom Tracker Node - Action Server execute error: %s", ex.what());
77  as_->setAborted();
78  }
79 }

86 void run()
87 {
88  ros::NodeHandle n;
89  ROS_INFO("Creating odom tracker action server");
90 
91  as_ = std::make_shared<Server>(n, "odom_tracker", boost::bind(&OdomTrackerActionServer::execute, this, _1), false);
92  ROS_INFO("Starting OdomTracker Action Server");
93 
94  as_->start();
95 
96  ros::spin();
97 }
